cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual tracking and proposes a novel method to address the problem of interference region in correlation filters. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the proposed method involves learning a correlation filter on a larger search region. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new approach to improve the performance of visual tracking. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with tracking objects in videos. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the proposed method can be applied to improve the performance of object tracking in robotics applications.
